00:34:12.184 --> 00:34:13.305
I could figure out a name.

00:34:13.365 --> 00:34:14.766
I don't know if it's going to work.

00:34:14.786 --> 00:34:16.188
We have a tiny apartment.

00:34:16.728 --> 00:34:18.290
And then I realized at that

00:34:18.402 --> 00:34:29.517
moment that he wasn't asking about my plan for being a parent, he was in fact offering to get us an abortion to take care of this in his mind problem.

00:34:29.537 --> 00:34:30.098
What do you want to do?

00:34:30.498 --> 00:34:35.545
And I said, well, I know I don't want you to do anything about the pregnancy.

