00:34:38.569 --> 00:34:48.242
And I assume he doesn't have very many, at that point in my life, I did assume he hadn't had very many young parents in there who found out they were pregnant and then just

00:34:48.546 --> 00:34:51.570
automatically didn't have their first reaction, want to terminate the pregnancy.

00:34:52.211 --> 00:34:55.235
And so he goes, you mean it takes his glass up?

00:34:55.275 --> 00:34:56.016
You want to keep it?

00:34:56.937 --> 00:34:57.057
It?

00:34:58.119 --> 00:35:04.347
And he's talking just so we're clear about my 15-year-old daughter who brings joy into our life every day, Olivia Skylusko.

00:35:04.407 --> 00:35:06.130
And for the record, we did want to keep it.

00:35:07.211 --> 00:35:13.239
But the way he said it was so cavalier and so nonchalant, like he was taking plates away from a table at a restaurant.

00:35:13.259 --> 00:35:13.940
Do you want to keep it?

00:35:13.960 --> 00:35:15.943
